        {
            "title": "美國貿易代表稱對中國第一階段經貿協定履行情況的調查將繼續推進",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普的首席貿易談判代表表示，儘管美中兩國達成了新的休戰協議，但美國仍將繼續一項調查，這將為對中國商品加徵新的關稅打開大門。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國貿易代表賈米森·格裡爾上周五對中國是否遵守川普首個總統任期內達成的第一階段經貿協定啟動調查。當時這一舉措被視作川普與中國國家主席習近平會晤時的一個潛在籌碼。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管兩國領導人在峰會上同意暫停提高關稅和收緊出口管制的計畫，但格裡爾周四在接受福克斯商業頻道採訪時表示，上述調查仍在繼續推進。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f576c117-d320-3fbf-a654-125efac1f6d0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「你的假設是正確的，」格裡爾對前川普經濟顧問、主持人Larry Kudlow表示，「我們今天並沒有解決美中關係中的全部問題。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：中美元首會晤緩和雙邊緊張關係 就關稅、稀土等達成休戰協議</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國決定不暫停該調查，這意味著一旦與習近平達成的協議破裂，川普仍有對中國實施新關稅報復的手段。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：[深度]中美握手休戰為長期爭霸蓄勢 取捨之間彰顯中國博弈之底氣</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Tariff Probe to Continue Despite Trump-Xi Deal, Greer Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%AC%AC-%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E7%B6%93%E8%B2%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%AE%9A%E5%B1%A5%E8%A1%8C%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E7%9A%84%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%B0%87%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%B2-221024446.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-31 07:21:31",
